description:
※這個樣式表，光點安裝是會破圖的！
與 NGID、ID 查詢、Komica 通知 相容，Chrome, Firefox 可正常渲染。
<a href="https://i.imgur.com/LYI3d5o.gifv" target="_blank">示範影片</a>

1. 為什麼會破圖？因為，你還要自己加上面兩句語法。<a href="https://i.imgur.com/1o5lbWw.gifv" target="_blank">教學影片</a>
2. 為什麼要你加？因為，這個網站禁止引用第三方的樣式，所以只能讓大家自己編輯。
3. 為什麼做這個？因為，無聊看到有人在說前端醜，就稍微試做了一下。

<h3>好，到底要加什麼？</h3>
→ 新建空白樣式表，命名為 Komica-MD-Driver，並匯入以下語法:
@-moz-document regexp("(http://|https://).*komica.org.*"), regexp("(http://|https://).*komica2.net.*") {
  @import url("https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/material-design-iconic-font/2.2.0/css/material-design-iconic-font.min.css");
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanstc.css");

css:
@-moz-document regexp("(http://|https://).*komica.org.*"), regexp("(http://|https://).*komica2.net.*") {

/* ？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？
 * 因為自動更新，導致跑版了嗎？
 * 如果你還沒創建一個新的 MD-Driver 樣式表，那現在來創造一個吧～
 * 方法就是將之前那二行多的引用語法貼到新的樣式表，並取名為 "MD-Driver"。
 * 
 * 語法在哪裡：
 * 進網頁找說明區塊，就會看到引用語法。
 * https://userstyles.org/styles/163901/komica-material-design-almost
 * 
 * 然後照著影片，動手做：
 * 影片就在網頁的說明中。
 * ？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？
 */

*
{
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
}

a:link, a:visited, .qlink, .text-button, .ngid-text-button, 
.text-button.ngid-context * {
    color: #548698; 
    transition: .2s ease-out;
}

a:hover, .ngid-text-button:hover{
    color: #33ABD8;
}

input, textarea
{
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif !important;
}


input {
    height: 30px;
    padding: 0px;
    color: #EEE;
}


input[type="text"],
textarea {
background: #383B40;
    color: #eee;
}

input[disabled="disabled"]{
    box-shadow: none;
    background: #282A2E;
}

input + input {
    margin-left: 3px;
}

/* Hide warning text */
div#postinfo {
    text-align: left;
    opacity: .1;
    transition: 5s cubic-bezier(1,.12,.81,.98);
} div#postinfo:active {
    opacity: 1;
    transition: none;
} div#postinfo:hover {
    transition: .5s;
    opacity: 1;
}


    /* Hover NAV Bar */

div#toplink:before {
   background: rgb(202, 77, 125);
   content: "≡";
   color: #eee;
   display: block;
   font-size: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 45px;
   width: 50px;
   height: 50px;
   position: fixed;
   right: 20px; 
   bottom: 20px;
   border-radius: 50%;
    transition: .2s;
    z-index: 9999;
} div#toplink:hover:before {
    opacity: 0;
} div#toplink {
    z-index: 9999;
   position: fixed;
   right: 0px;
   bottom: 0px;
   padding: 0 16px 80px 0;
   font-size: 0; 
   height: 0;
   overflow-y: hidden;
   transition: none;
   max-width: 50px;
} div#toplink:after {
   background: pink;
   display: none;
} div#toplink:hover {
    height: auto;
    max-width: unset;
    min-width: 120px;
    background: rgb(202, 77, 125);
    outline: 100vw solid rgba(0,0,0,.2);
    /*border-top-left-radius: 10px;*/
    transition: .5s;
    padding: 20px 16px 80px 20px;
} div#toplink a {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: none;
   font-size: 16px; 
    display: block;
    padding: 0 0 4px 0;
    color: #eee;
    padding-right: .5em;
} div#toplink a:first-child {
    padding-top: 4px;
} div#toplink:hover a {
   opacity: 1;
    transition: .1s ease-out;
    
} div#toplink a:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    margin-right: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
}




/* Main Start */

#header h1 {
    color: #C5C8C6;
} #header h1:before {
    content: "#";
    font-size: 90%;
} #header h1 + hr {
    display: none;
}

hr{
    border: 0; height: 1px; background: #333; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #ccc, #333, #ccc);
}

/* MD Checkbox */

input[type="checkbox"]{
    vertical-align: top;
    margin: auto 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0;
}


/*.post input[type="checkbox"] {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: .2s;
    position: relative;
    bottom: 7px;
}

.post:hover input[type="checkbox"],
.post input[type="checkbox"]:checked
{
    opacity: 1;
}*/

input[type="checkbox"] +label:before,
input[type="checkbox"] +.hide+label:before,
.post input[type="checkbox"] + span:before{
    z-index: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    content: "";
    vertical-align: top;
    background: rgba(100,100,100,.5);
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: .2s ease-in-out;
    margin-left: -20px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
}input[type="checkbox"]:checked +label:before,
input[type="checkbox"]:checked +.hide+label:before,
.post input[type="checkbox"]:checked + span:before{
    background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABIAAAASCAQAAAD8x0bcAAAAZUlEQVR4AWMYWuC/zP9D/xUJKXnw/9V/FXxKJMBKNPAruY1FyX8BJLYodiWO/z/9t4MruY7Vov88/0/8//rfGMgSQijBpuzc/w//Hf5f+v8Oj3P/8wOV/Qcq0QXx8Ck7AFQyRAAAcPlKRO/0WqEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=');
    background-color:#CA4D7D; 
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px #CA4D7D;
}

.post input[type="checkbox"]{
    width: 20px;
    margin-left: 0px;
    margin-right: 0px;
    left: 5px;
} .post input[type="checkbox"] + span:before {
    margin-right: 2px;
}



#postform_tbl tr td:first-child{
    min-width: 30px;
    padding-top: 4px;
    text-align: center;
    vertical-align: top;
    background: transparent;
}

/*#postform_tbl input[type="checkbox"]{
    vertical-align: top;
}*/


#postform_tbl tr td b{
    font-size: 0;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font";
}

#postform_tbl tr b:before{
    font-size: 20pt;
}

#postform_tbl tr:nth-child(1) b:before{
    content:"\f1ab";
}

#postform_tbl tr:nth-child(2) b:before{
    content:"\f207";
}

#postform_tbl tr:nth-child(3) b:before{
    content:"\f158";
}

#postform_tbl tr:nth-child(4) b:before{
    content:"\f17f";
}

#postform_tbl textarea#fcom{
    /*height: 180px !important;
    width: 500px !important;*/
    min-height: 100px;
    
    
}
#postform_tbl textarea#fcom:focus{
    /*height: 180px !important;
    width: 500px !important;*/
    transition: none;
    min-height: 300px !important;
}

#postform_tbl textarea#fcom:hover {
    transition: none;
}

#postform_tbl input[type="submit"]:hover{
    box-shadow: none;
    /*margin: 202px 0px 0 220px;*/
    margin: 2px;
}

#postform_tbl input[type="submit"]:active{
    background-color: #843251;
    box-shadow: none;
}

#postform_tbl input[type="submit"]{
    margin: 0px;
    
    position: absolute;/*
    margin: 200px 0px 0 218px;*/
    font-size: 0;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-image:   url('data:image/png;base64,');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 30px 30px;
    background-position: center center;
}

input, textarea {
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 0px solid;
    min-height: 30px;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 5px;
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    transition: .2s;
}

#postform_tbl input[type="text"],
#postform_tbl textarea {
    min-width: 350px;
}

#postform_tbl input:focus,
#postform_tbl textarea:focus{
    
    box-shadow: 0 0 2pt 1pt rgb(202, 77, 125);
}



input[type="submit"],
input[type="button"]{
    
    transition: .2s;
    background: rgb(202, 77, 125);
    width: 60px;
    font-size: 12pt;
}

input[type="submit"]:hover,
input[type="button"]:hover{
    box-shadow: 0 0 2pt 1pt rgb(202, 77, 125);
}input[type="submit"]:active,
input[type="button"]:active{
    background: #9E3C62;
} input[type="submit"]:focus,
input[type="button"]:focus{
    background: #9E3C62;
}




textarea {
    padding-top: 5px;
}


.thread {
    
}

.post {
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 10px;
}

.post.threadpost {
    top: 0;
}

.post, .post.reply {
    
}

.post:not(.threadpost) {
    
}

.post.threadpost 
{
    display: table;
    
    
    max-width: 700px;
    background: rgba(100,100,100,.4);
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    
}

.post.threadpost + hr,
.post.reply + hr{
    visibility: hidden;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

.post.threadpost .post-head {
    display: table-header-group;
    /*position: relative;
    top: 10px*/;
}

.post .file-text{
    opacity: 0.05;
    transition: .2s;
    padding-left: 2em;
}

.post:hover .file-text {
    opacity: 1;
}

.post .img {
    position: relative;
    left: 1em;
    
}

/* 圖片 放大 全螢幕 */
.post img.expanded-element.expanded-close {
    
    position: fixed;
    -webkit-transform: translate(-50%, -50%); 
    left: 50vw;
    top: 50vh;
    z-index: 999;
    border: 100vw solid rgba(0,0,0,.7);
}


.post-head {
    
}

.post.reply {
    
}


.file-thumb {
    display: inline-block;
}

img.img {
    
}

.warn_txt2 {
    margin-left: 5px;
    cursor: default;
    /*color: #548698;
    text-shadow: 0px 0px 8px rgba(90,90,90,.5);*/
    background: rgba(84,134,152,.5);
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.25);
    color: #eee;
    font-size: 25px;
    
    border-radius: 2px;
} .warn_txt2:hover {
    
}


.warn_txt2 .-expand-thread.text-button, .warn_txt2 .-collapse-thread.text-button {
    
    transition: .6s ease-in;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #548698;
    color: #eee;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    font-size: 0px;
    display: block;
    float: left;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font";
    margin: 0 0 10px 10px;
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    transform: rotate(0deg);
} .warn_txt2 .-expand-thread.text-button:hover, .warn_txt2 .-collapse-thread.text-button:hover {
    /*color: unset;*/
    transform: rotate(-180deg);
    box-shadow: -2px -1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
} .warn_txt2 .-expand-thread.text-button:active, .warn_txt2 .-collapse-thread.text-button:active {
    transform: rotate(-180deg);
    box-shadow: none;
    position: relative;
    left: 2px;
    top: 1px;
}

.warn_txt2 .-expand-thread.text-button::after {
    font-size: 40px;
    content: "\f312";
    margin-right: 2px;
}

.warn_txt2 .-collapse-thread.text-button::after {
    font-size: 40px;
    content: "\f311";
    margin-right: 2px;
}

.rlink {
    float: left;
}

.rlink, .rlink a,
.-del-button, .-del-button a
{
    font-size: 0px;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font";
}

.rlink a:after {
    font-size: 30px;
    content: "\f263";
    
    
}

.-del-button {
    float: right;
}

.-del-button a:after {
    font-size: 30px;
    content: "\f162";
    margin-right: 6px;
}

.qlink { /* ID No. */
    font-size: 18px;
    vertical-align: top;
    margin-right: 4px;
    color: #CA4D7D;
    
}

.post-head .qlink {
    float: right;
}

.post-head span:not(.qlink):not(.rlink){
    cursor: default;
}

.post-head .title{
    font-size: 20px;
}

.id {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    
    vertical-align: top;
    text-decoration: underline;
    float: left;
}

div.post-head span {
    vertical-align: top;
}

.now, .now+span { /* post timestring */
    color: #66696B;
    
} .now+span:after {
    white-space: pre;
    content: '\A';
}


/*.post-head > .qlink:before {
    content: "\A";
    white-space: pre;
}*/

.backquote-count {
    line-height: 20px;
}



.post {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 600px;
}

.reply {
    margin: 5px 0;
}
.post.reply {
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    
}

.post-head {
    margin-bottom: 3em;
}

.post .quote{
    margin: 1em 2em 1em 2em;
}

.post a.-expand-line{ /* 展開文章 */
    font-size: 0;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font";
} .post a.-expand-line:before{
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
    margin-top: 5px;
    transition: .2s;
    content: "\f3b4";
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #CA4D7D;
    color: #fff;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    font-size: 30px;
    line-height: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    opacity: 1;
    position: relative;
    left: 0px;
    top: 0px;
} .post a.-expand-line:hover:before {
    left: 1px;
    top: 2px;
    opacity: 1;
    box-shadow: none;
    /*font-size: 40px;*/
} .post a.-expand-line:active:before {
    /*font-size: 38px;*/
    box-shadow: none;
    opacity: 0.1;
}

input[type="checkbox"]:checked:after {
  
}
input[type="checkbox"]:checked:after {
  
}
input[type="checkbox"]:disabled:before {
  
}
input[type="checkbox"]:disabled:checked:before {
  
}

/* footer */
#header, #postform,
div#del, div#page_switch, #footer{
    background-color: #1D1F21;
    border: 1px solid #1D1F21;
    
    color: #C5C8C6;
    box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px #1D1F21;
}

div#del > table{
    float: none !important;
    margin: 10px auto 10px auto;
}

div#del > table td{
    font-size:0;
}

div#del > table td label[for="onlyimgdel"]{
    font-size: 12pt;
}

div#del > table td input[type="submit"]{
    font-size: 0;
    width: 30px;
    background-size: 25px 25px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center center;
    background-image:  url('data:image/png;base64,');
}

div#del > table td input[name="pwd"] {
    vertical-align: top;
    width: 150px;
    background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' version='1.1' height='30px' width='150px'><text x='5' y='20' fill='darkgrey' font-size='16'>TripKey</text></svg>");
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
} div#del > table td input[name="pwd"]:focus {
    vertical-align: top;
    background-image: none;
}

div#page_switch table{
    border: none !important;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #282A2E;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
}

div#page_switch table tr{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
}

div#page_switch input[type="submit"]{ /* Next Page Button */
    font-size: 0;
}

div#page_switch td {
    font-size: 0;
    min-width: 30px;
    
} div#page_switch td b {
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 28px;
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    color: #aaa;
    background: #111;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 30px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 12pt;
    font-weight: normal;
}
div#page_switch td a {
    vertical-align: top;
    font-size: 10pt;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    transition: .2s;
    border-radius: 0%;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    line-height: 28px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    
} div#page_switch td a:last-child {
    
}div#page_switch td a:hover {
    border-radius: 20%;
    /*border: 1px solid #CA4D7D;*/
    box-shadow: 0 0 2pt 1pt rgb(202, 77, 125);
    color: rgb(202, 77, 125);
    transform: scale(1.2);
} div#page_switch td a:active {
    transform: scale(1);
}

div#page_switch td:first-child form input {
    background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' version='1.1' height='30px' width='30px'><text x='3' y='24' fill='white' font-size='30'>⏴</text></svg>");
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
} div#page_switch td:last-child form input {
    background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' version='1.1' height='30px' width='30px'><text x='0' y='24' fill='white' font-size='30'>⏵</text></svg>");
    background-position: center center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
} div#page_switch td form input:active {
    
}


/* Extension: NGID Appended Button */

.text-button.ngid-context
{
    font-size: 0px;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font";
    float: right;
}

.text-button.ngid-context:after {
    font-size: 30px;
    content: "\f15b";
    margin-right: 4px;
}

.text-button.ngid-context div {
    font-size: 13px;
}

.ngid-context-menu {
    background-color: rgba(225,225,54,.95);
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 2px 1px 2px rgba(17,17,17,.5);
}

/* Extension: ID Query Appended Button */
.thread .post span[class^="id_"] > a[href*="www.homu-api.com/search?id="]:after{
    font-size: 30px;
    font-family: "Material-Design-Iconic-Font" !important;
    content: "\f200";
    float: right;
}

.thread .post span[class^="id_"]{
    background: none !important;
    border: 0px !important;
    font-size: 0px;
}

}
